戰，但實際上就靜雞雞殖民，靜靜雞買曬你啲地買曬你啲資產，到咗人口同資源上都佔據咗一定數量，國家內部權力就自然比中國人掌控，但係係國際外交上依然冇正式宣戰，只係啲無聊口水戰，不過內部已經比中國人佔領咗。<br />\n佢地最恐怖係好似寄生蟲咁靜靜雞由內部搞掂你，而唔係同你正面鬥過你死我活。"},{"pid":"03cd957c73d6306b823c768e82f397a2d93a0a84","tid":396871,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請唔好侮辱優越嘅日耳曼民族</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://wiki.komica.org/images/5/5a/Img11135.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.komica.org%2Fimages%2F5%2F5a%2FImg11135.jpg&h=5e0fd70b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"008fced70ee2a7b399891b730601c4533b079805","tid":396871,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>條友識唔識嫁 年輕一代愛國？ 你試下比本美國護照佢仲愛唔愛國</blockquote><br />\n佢應該未聽過「美軍來了我帶路」呢句野</blockquote><br />\n但確實有部分人真係去到納粹果下咁極端<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而且呢一班人真係係社會帶動緊一鼓咁樣既風氣， 令到主流社會都開始接近佢地既價值觀。。。</blockquote><br />\n連登仔唔會明"},{"pid":"1b450964dfee91af952fcae2d2c14e942004d974","tid":396871,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T06:00:11.000Z","msg":"拎德國同中國比真係侮辱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c021c6ee99dce1a9b6731bc0732a84156f531b8","tid":396871,"uid":10538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T06:00:51.000Z","msg":"年輕一代如此愛國，幾乎是極端民族主義者了。<br />\n雖遠必誅～"},{"pid":"aae4c8f44a509b2c32b610b9b5f8d4be776b4c3e","tid":396871,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T06:01:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我早一排先講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該話早排我都講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"h